div.h1: Expression Precedence: How AND/OR Are Parsed

div.p: AND binds tighter (like multiplication) evaluated first
OR binds looser (like addition) evaluated later
Use parentheses to override: sql -- Force OR first: (a OR b) AND c
-- Default (AND first): a OR b AND c
Naive interpretation: Evaluate left-to-right (a OR b) AND c
SQL precedence rules: AND binds tighter than OR a OR (b AND c)
